Special event clearways will be in place at the following locations to facilitate rail replacement bus operations for Metro North West trackwork:

  • Railway St, southbound between Day St and Help St, and
  • Brown St, westbound between Railway St and Pacific Hwy.

A no-stopping zone will also be in place northbound on Railway St between Brown St and Help St during this time.

Special event clearways are strict no-parking zones and also apply to local residents and TfNSW Mobility Parking Permit holders. Vehicles left in a clearway will be towed and a fee applies.

If your vehicle is towed, you can search your vehicle registration on the Find My Car website to find its new location, or alternatively call 132 701 to speak to an operator.
